name: mod_wsgi 4.1.0
body:
For details on this release see:
- http://modwsgi.readthedocs.org/en/latest/release-notes/version-4.1.0.html

This version marks the start of renewed development on mod_wsgi after a long hibernation. It introduces the new mod_wsgi express admin script for easier running of Apache/mod_wsgi.

With this version the version numbering scheme swaps to an X.Y.Z format instead of the older X.Y format.

name: mod_wsgi 3.5 (Security Release)
body:
For details on this release see:
- http://modwsgi.readthedocs.org/en/latest/release-notes/version-3.5.html

**Note that version 3.5 of mod_wsgi contains a fix for a security related issue. It is recommended that prior versions of mod_wsgi not be used.**
